                      <span>2001-07-02</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book has a great collection of drawings from various geogrraphies of India. They are all small in size and most of them are simple to draw or practice. I bought this book for my daughter who loves to sketch. She really enjoys spending time recreating some of the designs. Ajit Mookerjee did a nice job of compiling all these designs into one book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great Book For Mehendi Designs and Patterns</div>
