                    </div>
                    <span>Although the book has a lot of drawings that are not flat line drawings which can be used for mehendi, it has an excellent selection of line drawings which make beautiful mehendi art.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">great book, though some of the drawings are low quality</div>
